Step 1) Create a new partition of ext3 type(Hex code 83), size 800 MB and mount it permanently on /extdata.

Step 2) Create a new partition of vfat type(Hex code c), size 500 MB and mount it persistently on /windata.

Step 3) Create a another partition of xfs type, size 700 MB and mount it persistently on /xfsdata.

Step 4) Create a another partition of ext4 type, size 900 MB and mount it persistently on /ext4data.

SWAP PRACTICE
--------------

step 5) create an additional swap partition(Hex code 82) of 700 MB. Mount it permanently.

